{
  "id": "657327920960060024b6dfcf",
  "title": "Heptabaseの\"メタアプリ\"",
  "created": 1702045587,
  "updated": 1702046472,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "657327920960060024b6dfcf",
      "text": "Heptabaseの\"メタアプリ\"",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045587,
      "updated": 1702045592
    },
    {
      "id": "65732792b8bbfc000050f220",
      "text": "[https://nesslabs.com/heptabase-featured-tool Interview with Alan Chan, co-founder of Heptabase • Ness Labs]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045587,
      "updated": 1702045589
    },
    {
      "id": "65732795b8bbfc000050f222",
      "text": ">how we can solve the problem of interoperability across use cases and across applications is that I want Heptabase to eventually become a system where people can build and launch their own “[meta-apps]” on top of it.",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045589,
      "updated": 1702045627
    },
    {
      "id": "6573289eb8bbfc000050f22b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045855,
      "updated": 1702045855
    },
    {
      "id": "6573289eb8bbfc000050f22c",
      "text": "よくわからんけど適当に解釈",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045855,
      "updated": 1702045916
    },
    {
      "id": "657327bbb8bbfc000050f223",
      "text": " [Heptabase]の開発者いわく、「みんなが[Heptabase]の『meta-apps』を作ることでさまざまなユースケースに対応できるようにしたい」",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045628,
      "updated": 1702045890
    },
    {
      "id": "657328d6b8bbfc000050f22f",
      "text": " meta-appsでは、Heptabaseとは全く違うUIや機能でHeptabaseに書いた情報を扱う",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045911,
      "updated": 1702045955
    },
    {
      "id": "65732811b8bbfc000050f228",
      "text": " \t作ってあるカードやホワイトボードをそのまま利用できる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045714,
      "updated": 1702046472
    },
    {
      "id": "65732910b8bbfc000050f230",
      "text": " meta-apps同士ももちろん簡単に連携可能",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702045969,
      "updated": 1702046094
    },
    {
      "id": "65732947b8bbfc000050f232",
      "text": " イメージ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702046024,
      "updated": 1702046026
    },
    {
      "id": "6573299fb8bbfc000050f235",
      "text": " \tプラグインの上位互換",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702046111,
      "updated": 1702046118
    },
    {
      "id": "65732931b8bbfc000050f231",
      "text": "\t\t これなら(Notionの凝り性なカスタマイズやObsidianのプラグインのような)複雑さをプロダクト自体にはもたらさない可能性がある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702046002,
      "updated": 1702046203
    },
    {
      "id": "65732a23b8bbfc000050f239",
      "text": "\t\t \t[設定項目が多ければ多いほどユーザー体験の向上に繋がるわけではない]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702046244,
      "updated": 1702046247
    },
    {
      "id": "65732957b8bbfc000050f233",
      "text": "\t Heptabaseがmeta-appsを動かすOSとなる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1702046040,
      "updated": 1702046076
    }
  ]
}